Class Specie

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.config.Variable
com.pandora.config.species.abstractions.Specie
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
AqueousSpecie, SedimentarySpecie
public abstract class Specie extends Variable implements SpecieConfiguration, SpecieLogic
The Specie abstract class extends the Variable class and implements both the SpecieConfiguration and SpecieLogic interfaces. It serves as a base class for concrete implementations of biogeochemical species, providing a common structure for species configuration, logic, and variable behavior.
